      "title": "On inversion of convolution integral operators on a finite interval",
      "abstract": "The Gohberg-Heinig inversion formula for convolution operators on a finite interval is computed explicitly for the case when the kernel function is given by k(t)=Ce tA B, whereA,B, and C are matrices of appropriate sizes."
